HEADWORD: Subnotation
<hw>Sub`no*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>subnotatio</ets> a signing underneath, fr. <ets>subnotare</ets> to
subscribe; <ets>sub</ets> under + <ets>notare</ets> to note or
mark.]</ety> <def>A rescript.</def> <rj><au>Bouvier.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
